Author: throwawayedfeelz
Text: I'm ashamed to admit it but in the past 8 or so months of relapse I've accumulated almost 10,000 bodycheck photos... I always look back and compare them to my first LW pictures and I can't help it, can't help but try recreating them either? Occasionally I see the amount of storage just bodychecks take up and sometimes it hits me that that's... Not normal. That I can't walk past a mirror with my phone in hand without having to check if I look the same as I did a few hours previous, or a few days prior, or next to my LW... ED's are exhausting, I'm so sorry...
